d_lr = 2e-4

    data_dir, 
    bs=bs, 
    data_pct=data_pct,
    g_lr=g_lr, 
    d_lr=d_lr,
    device='cuda', 
    pretrained_damsm_path=pretrained_damsm_path,
    smooth_lambda=smooth_lambda,
    noise_sz=noise_sz,
)
